[[div class="notation table2 tableb widetable"]]

= [[span class="titled"]]INTRUSION LOG 9923-1:[[/span]] Across the Threshold

-----

**LOCALITY:** Nx-9923 imbrication zone.

**CERTAINTY RATING:** 89%

**RATIONAL ALIGNMENT:** 1 = 2

**PORTRAITURE:** In the Bordergarden of Reckless Abandon, there are many low miracles and mild infoallergens. Bald marble heads the size of tables extrude from the ground at strange angles. Something with a body like a globe shuffles about the ceiling, occasionally dribbling quasi-slime from its Panama Canal. Limbless shadows shift and strut across the walls. A [[span class="text-glow"]]distant melody[[/span]] wheedles along the edge of hearing.

----

||~ «BEGIN DIA-LOG» ||

//<Agent Quatrain uploads to the imbrication zone through the primary point of ingress ([[[scp-6445 | ⌘]]]). It surveys the scene, shielding its eyes with its hand as if looking across a great distance.>//

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]What a drab and unmemorable locale! Certainly one for the Foundation's scrapbooks, wouldn't you say?[[/span]]

**SiteCommand 1:** Reminder that official Foundation communication channels may not be used for off-topic chatter.

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]Numerous apologies for the breach of protocol. Permission to kill myself?[[/span]]

**SiteCommand A:** Negative. Determining a path to MEDIATOR is currently of the utmost priority.

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]Understood.[[/span]] [[span class="id"]]Now, portal or port hole... where would I be?[[/span]]

//<Officer Quatrain slowly circumnavigates the imbrication zone, prodding at anything within reach with the toe of its boot. It comes into view of a surface like a horizontal pond, if ponds were primarily made out of barbed wire and snapped rosaries.>// 

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]Oh, my! Who’s this dashing fellow?[[/span]]

//<There is a figure stranding in the surface of the not-pond. It is pale, gangling dangerously, and dressed in an eggshell blue hospital gown, feet bare. Violet wires dart in and out of its skin like vipers. Its face is obscured by papier-mâché wings and an oversized mailbag is slung over one shoulder.>//

**SiteCommand 1:** That’s you. It’s your reflection.

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]That’s me? Could it be that my monopoly of self is at an end?[[/span]] [[span class="superego"]]I don’t know if I’m ready for that kind of business relationship...[[/span]]

**SiteCommand A:** Only you are you. Reflections are illusions; deceptions of visual wavelengths and pattern recognition. It’s not real.

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Deceptions...[[/span]]

//<Counselor Quatrain rests its hand on the knotpond’s surface, marveling as rosaries trickle over and around its fingers. Its mirror image does the same, expressionless.>//

**SiteCommand 1:** //<Muffled.>// Are you sure this is a good idea? It didn’t even recognize its own reflection.

**SiteCommand A:** //<Muffled.>// We don’t want any precognitions clouding it. It’s an unavoidable hazard.

**SiteCommand 1:** //<Muffled.>// And that’s what the Underwatch Council wants? I //like// clouds. How else would we have acid rain?

**SiteCommand A:** //<Muffled.>// I hear you, but they were fairly clear about this -- insofar as they are clear about anything. I could show you the vibro-stenographies if you’d like?

**SiteCommand 1:** //<Muffled.>// No, no, it’s fine. I should leave the left-braining to you. //<Unmuffled.>// Keep searching, Inquisitor Quatrain. The entrance proper to Nx-9923 must be somewhere nearby.

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]Yes, sir. Sirs.[[/span]]

//<Investigator Quatrain extricates its hand from the knotpond -- when it does, the reflection turns and melts away. Investigating, it makes its way to the largest of the marble heads.>//

[[include :scp-wiki:component:image-block
|name=imbrication.png
|caption=Nx-9923 imbrication zone. Estimated pictorial accuracy: low.
|width=250px
|align=right]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Hmmmmmm.[[/span]]

//<Specialist Quatrain plucks out the head's left eye and licks it.>//

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]Silicon.[[/span]]

//<It licks the marble eye twice more.>//

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]Copper. Gold.[[/span]]

//<It licks the eye again.>//

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]And is that...?[[/span]]

//<It licks the eye.>//

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Yes, fluoride glass![[/span]] [[span class="ego"]]This must be the place.[[/span]]

**SiteCommand 1:** Excellent work.

**SiteCommand A:** Be advised that we’ll be cutting contact once you’re in. You’ll be on your own from here on out.

**Quatrain:**   [[span class="ego"]]Understood. Thank you for everything, sirs.[[/span]] [[span class="superego"]]I won’t let you down.[[/span]]

**SiteCommand 1:** Loading cryptocatalyst. Preparing for deliverance.

**SiteCommand A:** Delivering data package now. Good luck.

//<Ozone sparks. The head's mouth yawns open. Six letters have been chiseled into its tombstone teeth:>//

[[div class="papernote"]]
[[=]]
++ {{**M     E     D**}}
++ {{**I     U     M**}}
[[/=]]
[[/div]]

//<Sergeant Quatrain is swallowed whole.>//

||~ «END DIA-LOG» ||

[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="jotting" style="border: solid 0.3rem rgb(var(--general-border-color));"]]

[[span class="titled"]]UNCONTAINMENT PROCEDURES:[[/span]] SCP-9923 must not be contained, on account of it being too wide to carry up the stairs, not matching Site-⌘'s decor, and giving the entire human race a fatal brain hemorrhage whenever we yank on it too hard.[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]][[span class="titled"]]SAPIENTIA:[[/span]] Item is entangled with human consciousness and consequently cannot be contained.[[/span]] Resources are to be focused on the exploration of Nx-9923 and detainment of MEDIATOR.

Embedded printers/printer repairmen within [[[church-of-the-broken-god-hub | GoI-004C ("Church of Maxwellism")]]], GoI-004E ("Engineers of the Fifth Eschaton"), and [[[scp-4485 | GoI-4485 ("HANSARP")]]] have been instructed to seek out information regarding SCP-9923 whenever possible, provided that it does not put their cover at risk.

It's now safe to turn off your computer.

[[span class="titled"]]DESCRIPTION:[[/span]] SCP-9923 is a partially fulfilled equation and nothing more:

[[div class="table4 tableb widetable"]]
||~ VIRTUAL SPACE + HEADSPACE = MEDIUM ||
[[/div]]

[[/div]]

