= [[span class="titled"]]INTRUSION LOG 9923-3:[[/span]] Causeway Crypticism

-----

**LOCALITY:** Nx-9923 - Neoplasmic Chrysalid

**CERTAINTY RATING:** 0.005%

**RATIONAL ALIGNMENT:** █ = █ = █ = 5 = █

**PORTRAITURE:** As the dribbling sun creeps across the undernoon sky, something terrible is on the cusp of becoming born. The signs are there for any with the ears to hear. It is in the psychic geometry of the crowd, the heaving swelter of their churn. An index pushing through a throat without breaking skin. It is in the holes, the null zones where datum and dream slips through. Forgetting moves and grooves as fast as a racehorn, remember? And it is in you,[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]][[span class="titled"]]YOU:[[/span]] Yes, you.[[/span]] as well. The house called city blisters towards its breaking point.

[[div class="blockquote subport"]]

**SUBPORTRAITURE:** Listen. If you are quiet, really quiet. If you crawl into some unfamiliar corner or coronary artery. If you open your ears so wide that they become eyes. You might be able to hear it, just behind the seashell of your heartbeat. Like wind skimming the edge of a ragged wound. A hollow sound. A shout. A bad idea.

[[/div]]

The tide bends towards the brutalist. All is as it should be.

----

||~ «BEGIN DIA-LOG» ||

//<The corridor is immense and narrow, barely wide enough to walk. Call-Of-The-Mite extends from the theoretical ceiling like a bad vector, hanging barely a meter above the ground. Her neck is a crude stump; she cradles her serene and sleeping face in her arms. Flesh melts into unblemished marble seamlessly. Her [[span class="text-glow"]]voice[[/span]] is barely a breath.>//

**Call-Of-The-Mite:** Echoes. I hear echoes. Is somebody there?

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]Pardon me, //mademoiselle//. I seek MEDIATOR and this appears to be the only way forward.[[/span]] [[span class="id"]]So long as I still have this papyrine pulp in my teeth, anyway...[[/span]]

**Call-Of-The-Mite:** Do you seek? Or are you sought?

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]I //am// sorry for intruding. Should I k--[[/span]] [[span class="id"]]//<Ahem.>//[[/span]] [[span class="superego"]]That is to say, is there anything I can do to make this home invasion more comfortable for you?[[/span]]

**Call-Of-The-Mite:** Come closer, closer, and we'll see. //<Pause.>// Well, well. What a beautiful mask you have.

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]Ah, but you are mistaken, madam. These are wings.[[/span]]

[[include :scp-wiki:component:image-block
|name=vacant-corner.jpg
|caption=Vacant corner. Estimated pictorial accuracy: 90 degrees.
|width=250px
|align=right]]

**Call-Of-The-Mite:** I'm not talking about that. Not that.

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]What?[[/span]]

**Call-Of-The-Mite:** Your //mask//. Everyone has one. Everyone. 

//<Call-Of-The-Mite adjusts her grip on her head, tilting it slightly. For a moment, something verdant is half-glimpsed through the lines of her face.>//

**Call-Of-The-Mite:** You wouldn't be a person without it.

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Are masks a kind of container, for keeping one's person-ness inside themselves?[[/span]] [[span class="superego"]]Do they have spillproof lids? I'm awfully clumsy.[[/span]]

**Call-Of-The-Mite:** Close. That's very close. A thing ##green|**known**## is a thing ##green|**grown**##, after all. And are gardeners not the true masters of their flock? Without a mask, you'd certainly be in someone else's hands.

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]That's all well and good, but I really do need to be going...[[/span]] [[span class="ego"]]Could you kindly get out of my way? I'm on something of a deadline.[[/span]] [[span class="superego"]]If I don't hurry, I'll stop holding the line and start holding the... other thing.[[/span]]

**Call-Of-The-Mite:** Are you sure that's what you want? Are you sure? I am no warden. This path leads to nowhere and nothing.

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]If nowhere is where my quarry lies, then nowhere I must go![[/span]]

**Call-Of-The-Mite:** Quarry. Is that what you are for? To carve through stone? To hunt?

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]I--[[/span]]

**Call-Of-The-Mite:** No matter. The choice, the choice is already made. Whatever you do next... just be certain that's what you want. Be certain.

//<The scene freezes.>//

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]//Mademoiselle//?[[/span]]

//<Dir. Quatrain steps forward, hand raised in concern-- which promptly tears through the backdrop, sending Stagehand Quatrain tumbling into the next act.>//

||~ «END DIA-LOG» ||

[[/div]]

@@ @@

