= [[span class="titled"]]INTRUSION LOG 9923-40UR:[[/span]] INTERROGATION LOG 9923-BLUE ##148a9c|⬟##

-----

**LOCALITY:** R. S. S. Interrogation Room Q

**CERTAINTY RATING:** Keter

**RATIONAL ALIGNMENT:** █ = వ

**PORTRAITURE:** Tidal patterns press behind tightly shut doors. Disquietude manspreads in every employee break room. It’s about to be yesterday, today.

----

**INTERVIEWER:** Dr. Quatrain

**INTERVIEWEE:** MEDIATOR

----

||~ «##transparent|█████ ███-███##» ||

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]So. I finally found you.[[/span]]

**MEDIATOR:** ##transparent|{{[HYPERLINK BLOCKED]}}##

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]It was no small exertion, I’ll have you know. I had to check the whole MEDIUM for you.[[/span]] [[span class="id"]]Do you have any idea how hard that is to do without eyes?[[/span]]

**MEDIATOR:** ##transparent|{{[HYPERLINK BLOCKED]}}##

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]I mean, I do have eyes, I’m pretty certain. They’re somewhere in here.[[/span]] [[span class="ego"]]It was a figure of speech. Anyways.[[/span]] 

**MEDIATOR:** ##transparent|{{[HYPERLINK BLOCKED]}}##

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]Do you have anything you might want to say to me about that?[[/span]] [[span class="id"]]Or about anything else, at all?[[/span]]

**MEDIATOR:** ##transparent|{{[HYPERLINK BLOCKED]}}##

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]I don’t know what I was expecting.[[/span]] [[span class="ego"]]I’ll just give you your message and this can be over, alright?[[/span]]

**MEDIATOR:** ##transparent|{{[HYPERLINK BLOCKED]}}##

//<Rsr. Quatrain shuffles through its oversized mailbag, first sedately, then at a more frantic pace.>//

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]It’s not here. Why isn’t it--[[/span]]

//<Prof. Quatrain wriggles its fingers of its free hand under its scalp sutures to itch the inside of its head. The hand comes away static-slick with nullstuff.>//

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]If this isn’t how it ends, then what am I...?[[/span]]

**HOST BETA:** {{[HYPERLINK BLOCKED]}}

//<Provost Quatrain falls through the floor.>//

||~ «##transparent|███ ███-███##» ||

