||~ [[size 175%]]FILE 0/2[[/size]] ||
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[div class="notation table2 tableb widetable"]]

= [[span class="titled"]]INTRUSION LOG 9923-##transparent|█████##[[/span]]

-----

**LOCALITY:** Nx-9923 - Inside
 
**CERTAINTY RATING:** Absent

**RATIONAL ALIGNMENT:** 0 = 0

**PORTRAITURE:** A stage, lit by a [[span class="text-glow"]]single spotlight[[/span]]. The air smells of velvet and dust. Rows of empty seats stretch into darkness. There is nothing else.

----

||~ «##transparent|█████ ███-███##» ||

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]Ah, I can't believe I'm finally... wherever this is.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]What are you talking-- I mean, what am //I// talking about?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Hold on a moment. Something feels... off. It's almost as if--[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]We've separated?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]I think we have.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Or as separate as we are capable of.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]I never thought I'd feel like this again...[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]Does that make this a monologue, or a dialogue?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]A trialogue, perhaps?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]Just make sure it's not a pentalogue and I'll be happy. God, am I sick of the number five.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Hey, don't badmouth numbers like that. My great aunt was a negative integer.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]Sorry, I didn't mean to offend. Should I--[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]Let's try to stay on track, just in case one of those dulcineas are about.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Yes, where //are// we?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]We're inside, didn't you look at the locality descriptor?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]I just read the tales.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]The question we ought to be asking is //why// are we? Why was I-- was //we// put together?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]To conceptualize, I think.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]To contain. Put things in little boxes, then put those boxes in slightly larger boxes. And so on.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Yeah, that's what I said.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]Are we supposed to contain SCP-9923? Can such a thing be possible?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Are //we// possible?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]Of course not.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]So what? There are countless numbers between 1 and 2, but none of them will ever be 3.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]Not with that attitude they won't.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]Aren't you supposed to be the sad sack of the group?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]I was never "supposed" to be anything.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]So we //can// contain SCP-9923? SCP-005?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]I'm pretty sure it's a starfish.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Agree to disagree.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]Containment was never the only option. Why do you think we went through all that pain?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]I don't think there was a reason. Sometimes suffering is just suffering.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]I thought the forever torture was pretty okay. I mean, I didn't //love// it.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]I need you two to really think on this. We've been in here for... I don't know, millions of years? Billions? A couple of days? Plenty of time to get the lay of the land.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]Lay of the land? What are you //talking// about?[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="ego"]]I don't understand.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="id"]]I need to understand.[[/span]]

**Quatrain:** [[span class="superego"]]That's okay. I'll show you. Just take my hand.[[/span]]

